title: A Show Member Asks Bobby For A Favor + 90’s Country Songs We Think Are Essential + Bobby’s Mailbag: How To Deal With A Co-Worker Who Is Always Late

description:
Bobby never does this…but he lets someone one the show ask him for a big favor. We each share our pick for 90’s country songs that we think are essential to the decade. Bobby helps a listener who emailed in needing advice on a coworker who is always late and making work a nightmare.
